{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f3dd626edd","title":"给邓宝珊的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"33de50e933","index":0,"year":1944,"month":12,"day":22,"articleId":"f3dd626edd","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"书信","id":"2a70b5d939","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji3","name":"毛泽东文集第三卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"/books/wenji3.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji3":{"comments":[{"id":"2ca5500eae","publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"f3dd626edd","publication":{},"article":{},"index":1,"part_index":0,"offset":4,"text":"邓宝珊（一八九六——一九六八），甘肃天水人。当时任国民党军晋陕绥边区总司令。"},{"id":"61c160caef","publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"f3dd626edd","publication":{},"article":{},"index":2,"part_index":2,"offset":89,"text":"绍庭，即刘绍庭。抗日战争时期曾任陕甘宁边区参议会参议员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"57de143f6d","type":"title","text":"给邓宝珊的信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"f3dd626edd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2ca5500eae","type":"appellation","text":"宝珊先生吾兄左右：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"f3dd626edd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"61c160caef","type":"paragraph","text":"去年时局转换，先生尽了大力，我们不会忘记。八年抗战，先生支撑北线，保护边区，为德之大，更不敢忘。去秋晤叙，又一年了，时局走得很快，整个国际国内形势都改变了。许多要说的话，均托绍庭兄专诚面达。总之只有人民的联合力量，才能战胜外寇，复兴中国，舍此再无他路。如果要对八年抗战作一简单总结，这几句话，鄙意以为似较适当，未知先生以为然否？何时获得晤叙机会，不胜企望之至。专肃，敬祝健康！","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"f3dd626edd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5fb54b1dfd","type":"subtitle","text":"毛泽东 上十二月二十二日","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"f3dd626edd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"47c41af32d","type":"paragraph","text":"根据人民出版社一九八三年出版的","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"f3dd626edd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0606834be7","type":"paragraph","text":"《毛泽东书信选集》刊印。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"f3dd626edd","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":256,"end":256}}}},"__N_SSG":true}